Species of the genus Thressa Walker, 1860 from China (Diptera, Chloropidae)Abstract A review of the species of the genus Thressa from China is provided. The following four species are described as new to science: Thressa bimaculata sp. n., Thressa daiyunshana sp. n., Thressa foliacea sp. n. and Thressa longimaculata sp. n. One species, Thressa flavior (Duda), is recorded from China for the first time. A key to the species of the Thressa from China is given.